text: Jacob Frey ( ; born July 23, 1981) is an American politician. He is the mayor of Minneapolis, Minnesota. He is a member of the Minnesota Democratic-Farmer- Labor Party. He was elected to the Minneapolis City Council in 2013, representing the Third Ward.Helal, Liala (November 7, 2013) "Minneapolis demographics change; younger candidates shape new City Council", MPR News. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Mayors of Minneapolis Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
